## üí° Project Overview

**"Aggregating fragmented election information into one dashboard"**

During the presidential election, critical information such as news, polls, and candidate pledges was scattered across various platforms, making it difficult for voters to access. To address this, we developed an **Aggregator Service that collects and visualizes all election-related data in one place**.

We adopted **AWS Amplify (Serverless)** to minimize backend infrastructure costs and efficiently handle authentication and data synchronization. On the frontend, we utilized **MUI (Material UI)** and **Recharts** to build an intuitive, data-rich dashboard.

### üõ† Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** React, Styled Components, MUI (Material UI)
- **Visualization:** Recharts
- **Backend (Serverless):** AWS Amplify (Auth, API)
- **Crawling & Network:** Cheerio, Microlink, Axios

