### 3. Personalization (Bookmarks)

<ImageDescription src="/images/election-aggregator/5.webp" alt="Reading list"/>

Users can bookmark articles of interest. These bookmarks are synchronized to their personal storage in real-time via **Amplify API (GraphQL)**.

