Displays election news collected via Naver News API in a card format.

We enhanced information delivery by parsing and visualizing metadata (thumbnails, summaries) using **Microlink**.

### 5. Poll Charts

<ImageDescription src="/images/election-aggregator/13.webp" alt="Election poll page"/>

